lead_paragraph: Hunter Pence is healthy at last. Joe Panik has been back a few days from a concussion and is driving in runs again. The San Francisco Giants sure are starting to look like themselves again.

headline.print_headline: Giants Find Just Enough Offense for Rare Win Since Break
